description:
http://takingaimradio.com/ with Ralph Schoenman and Mya Shone.

A two part series which centers around the important 1975 article "The Gentlemen Killers of the CIA", by former NY Times correspondent Harrison Salisbury. Recorded in October, 2003 - the height of the so-called "War on Terror". 

For more related content, please visit: https://archive.org/details/@altviewstv-fanclub
